I just found a super cheap workaround.. 

You can just wrap the TextField in a Stack and add a colored container behind the TextField.

Like: 

```
Stack(
children: [
     Positioned.fill(
            child: DecoratedBox(
              decoration: BoxDecoration(
                color: appTheme.surfaceInput,
                borderRadius: borderRadius,
              ),
            ),
          ),
         yourTextField # filled:false,
]
)

```


